That's what I thought, so I
panicked, I panicked badly.

43:20.264 --> 43:21.641
But I didn't do it.

43:21.808 --> 43:23.856
I didn't kill Stoddart.

43:25.353 --> 43:27.447
I know you didn't.

43:48.960 --> 43:51.054
The professor
told me this word.

43:51.212 --> 43:53.260
Icelandic word
for elation.

43:53.422 --> 43:54.719
What, <i>glethi</i> ?

43:54.882 --> 43:57.305
<i>Glethi</i>, that's it.

43:57.468 --> 43:59.721
Sort of what
I'm feeling now.

43:59.887 --> 44:02.811
You and me, we could have helped
catch the person who did this.

44:02.974 --> 44:04.851
Yeah.

44:06.435 --> 44:08.779
I want to get drunk
or something.

44:08.938 --> 44:12.317
Yeah, you should do that.

44:12.483 --> 44:14.360
I haven't got
any drink at mine.

44:16.487 --> 44:18.364
Well, I have.

44:19.782 --> 44:21.625
Come to mine.

44:21.784 --> 44:23.206
Okay.

44:25.663 --> 44:27.506
<i>What are you looking for?</i>

44:27.665 --> 44:30.760
I believe Frank.
I believe Frank and Elena.

44:32.628 --> 44:35.757
I need to prove they didn't
do this terrible thing.

44:35.923 --> 44:37.971
What was Liam wearing
when you left him?

44:38.134 --> 44:39.977
Um, just pajamas.

44:40.136 --> 44:41.809
Do you know where they are?

44:41.971 --> 44:44.315
No, I couldn't find them.
Think, Jules.

44:44.473 --> 44:45.440
I don't know.

44:45.600 --> 44:47.227
Under the bed?

44:47.393 --> 44:50.192
No, I-I would have
found them there.

44:50.354 --> 44:52.948
Ah... Dan, talk to
me, what's going on?

45:05.786 --> 45:08.039
<i>In the little boy's bedroom.</i>

45:08.206 --> 45:10.755
Covered in blood.

45:10.917 --> 45:13.466
<i>Caked</i> in dried blood.

45:13.628 --> 45:15.847
Frank was
telling the truth.

45:18.716 --> 45:20.639
The frostbite.

45:20.801 --> 45:22.678
Something terrible
happened to him.

45:22.845 --> 45:26.349
The little boy was there when
Charlie Stoddart was murdered.

45:27.850 --> 45:29.727
He was right there.

45:34.273 --> 45:35.274
Dan?

45:36.734 --> 45:39.328
The window was open.

45:39.487 --> 45:41.489
Liam's bedroom window.

45:41.656 --> 45:44.284
Someone took him.

46:13.479 --> 46:15.356
♪♪

47:50.368 --> 47:52.211
At first I thought it
was a bone fragment.

47:52.370 --> 47:53.542
It's a fingernail.
Someone

47:53.704 --> 47:54.705
must have put that there!

47:54.872 --> 47:55.794
That is not him!

47:55.956 --> 47:57.299
Don't touch me!

47:57.458 --> 47:59.085
My feet are burning!

47:59.251 --> 48:01.674
Pettigrew made the scan
that was in this folder.

48:01.837 --> 48:04.135
Now the scan is gone
and Pettigrew is dead.

48:04.298 --> 48:05.550
<i>Where would a shaman
lay his hands</i>

48:05.716 --> 48:07.218
on half a pint
of murderer's blood?

48:07.385 --> 48:08.432
<i>Beyond human understanding,</i>

48:08.594 --> 48:09.686
<i>but that is what happened.</i>

48:09.845 --> 48:12.439
No witness, no motive,

48:12.598 --> 48:14.396
no crime.

48:14.558 --> 48:16.276
<i>We have the murderer for sure.</i>

48:16.435 --> 48:17.857
I want to go home.

48:18.020 --> 48:19.317
I just came to say
one thing to you.

48:19.480 --> 48:22.859
Stay the fuck away from me.

